  <name>Momentum Mouse</name>
  <summary>Smooth, natural scrolling for Linux</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Momentum Mouse brings smooth, natural scrolling to Linux desktop environments.
      It transforms the abrupt, jerky scrolling experience typical of mouse wheels
      into a fluid, momentum-based scrolling experience similar to modern trackpads.
    </p>
    <p>
      Configure settings via the GUI app or manually through command-line arguments
      or the config file at <code>/etc/momentum_mouse.conf</code>.
    </p>
  </description>

  <developer_name>Ash Martian</developer_name>
